io.hekate.codec

Interface JavaSerializable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface JavaSerializable
extends Serializable
    Marker interface for classes that should use the Java default serialization policy.

    Some Codecs can use this interface in order to enforce JDK default serialization on objects that implement this interface and bypass some internal optimizations.
